content.raw: This is a joke, right? After 17 hours ver25p02x4 e25e7baa-23c2-4f0a-8d86-6432077ed938 finished with `With no errors` \(note that there is not the word “Terminated”\) I can see 5 log files - one main and 4 robots as it used to be, and if I click `A10F…` I get `There are no logs to download`. This is for robot A and C, B works, D also works … my only hope is that “it is still in progress”??
